{"serial": "26006", "department_serial": 23, "code": "OS2014", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Fundamentals of Electronics II", "ch": "基礎電學II"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Yang, Tsung-Hsun"], "ch": ["楊宗勳"]}, "credits": 4, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["5", "6"]}, "loc": {"building": "IL", "room": "203"}}, {"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "IL", "room": "203"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "光電科學與工程學系", "en": "Department of Optics and Photonics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "部分英語", "en": "Partially English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 55, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程延續基本電子學理論(1)，第一部分將教導包括各種元件組合電路包括電流鏡/共源共柵電路/差動放大電路，並分析各電路之放大效應及頻率響應。\n培養學生利用簡化等效模型等分析工具，瞭解熟悉各種電路組合的工作模式(包含電晶體、場效電晶體等)，以及相關的基礎應用。\n第二部分介紹邏輯設計電路基本概念，包括邏輯閘設計、組合電路、時序電路設計。是光電、電子及電機工程之重要基礎課程之一，同時為進階積體電路設計之先修課程。", "en": "This course provides an introduction to the basic devices and circuits in modern electronics.  In continuity with Fundamentals of Electronics II.  Students will learn the basic combination circuits of BJTs and MOSFETs, including current mirrors / cascade circuits / differential circuits.  This is one of the fundamental and pre-requested courses in photonics, electronics and electrical engineering.\nStudents will learn how to analyze the basic knowledge of logic design.  Combining with CMOS circuits, fundamentals of logic operation will be given."}, "outline": {"ch": "1. 頻率響應分析 (續)\n-場效電晶體頻率響應 (回顧)\n-雙極性接面電晶體頻率響應\n2. 整合放大器電路分析\n- 電流鏡 / 疊接放大器\n- 整合放大器電路模型分析\n3. 差動放大器及多級放大器\n- 差動放大器特性\n- 差動放大電路及差模/共模訊號分析\n4. 回遺電路 / 功率放大器\n5. 數位電路介紹\n- 數位訊號/邏輯分析\n- 邏輯閘介紹\n6. 組合電路\n- 邏輯閘設計 / 應用\n- 電路簡化\n7. 時序電路\n- 正反器原理及設計\n- 時序電路設計", "en": "Fundamentals of Electronics II\nFrequency response\n- BJT / MOSFET\n- Circuit combination\nTransistor module\n- Current mirror\n- Differential amplifier\n- Cascode amplifier\n(Feedback)\n(Power amplifier)\nDigital circuit\n- CMOS circuits\n- Digital number system\nCombinatorial logic\n- Logic gates\nSequential logic\n- Latches / Flip-Flops"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“Microelectronic Circuits” 7th edition, Sedra / Smith\n“Digital Design – with an Introduction to the Verilog HDL, VHDL, and System Verilog,” \u000bby Mano ＆ Ciletti", "en": "“Microelectronic Circuits” 7th edition, Sedra / Smith\n“Digital Design – with an Introduction to the Verilog HDL, VHDL, and System Verilog,” \u000bby Mano ＆ Ciletti"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "30", "en": "30"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n實習/實驗", "en": ["Lecture", "", "Practical Training Lab"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "Homework – 25％\nMidterm I / II  – 25％ + 25％\nFinal – 25％\nAttendance (reference)", "en": "Homework5 – 25％\nMidterm I / II – 25％ + 25％\nFinal – 25％\nAttendance (reference)"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週二 15:00~18:00", "en": "TUE 15:00~18:00"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "基礎學科", "en": "基礎學科"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "專業知識", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "科學思辯", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "實驗能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "團隊合作", "rating": "(1)非常低", "assesments": ["無"]}, {"competencies": "外語能力與國際視野", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Professional Knowledge", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": "Scientific Thinking", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments"]}, {"competencies": "Hands-on Capability", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": "Team Work", "rating": "(1)VeryLow", "assesments": ["No assessment"]}, {"competencie